    "3.4.2 Question 8: is Undetectable.AI able to overcome AI detection systems?",
    "We investigated the association between authorship and the author identified by automatic AI detection systems.",
    "For this analysis, the stimuli were the ChatGPT texts and the Undetectable.AI texts (abbreviated as UND).",
    "To do so, we performed a χ 2 test between the two variables.",
    "This revealed a significant association between the two variables, χ 2 (1) = 7.37, p = 0.007."
  ],
